    <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--color-ink-mute);margin:0 0 8px;">The sequence below is deliberately short. Unrecoverable errors are not a case where extended self-troubleshooting helps &mdash; it usually makes the file worse. The priority is <strong>protect the file, attempt one round of automated repair, and escalate</strong>.</p>
